title: Departmental Fund Reports Macro
description: This was a Macro Program for UC San Diego's Donor and Gift Fund Stewardship Departmental Fund Reports. The Macro was designed to collate and sort Funds based on their Departments automatically with one click.

title: Project 1: Expository Visualization
description: This is an Expository Visualization of Average Hour of Sunshine in terms of Seasons and Quarters among a range of different cities across the US. The project was completed in DSC 106 at UC San Diego.

title: UC San Diego EconLab Research
description: This was a research project focused on how Chilean Firms use Trade Credit. I was in a research group under Economics Graduate Student Renata Abbott-Navarrete.
